reviews.review:
Very toxic game community:
-People cursing and reporting you for no reason;
-Premade lobby trolls;
-And full of little children calling you noob for killing them;
It's shame to give this game a thumbs down because has a lot of potential and a good leveling up system that will get you hooked(''Get it? Huh? Like a HOOKED surviver?'').
If you really wanna have a clean game seasion avoid pubs and gather another 4 friends to play with.
